      "value": "<p>Beginning at 7th level, you can condense part of your swarm into a focused mass that lifts you up. As a bonus action, you gain a flying speed of <strong>10 feet</strong> and can <strong>hover</strong>. This effect lasts for 1 minute or until you are incapacitated.</p>\n<p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a <strong>long rest</strong>.</p>",
